# 📝 Blog Cards Project

A simple responsive blog card project created with HTML and CSS.

The project contains two blog cards with images, icons and descriptions.

---

## 🚀 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Font Awesome
- Responsive Layout

---

